title: The Mandalorian Dark Trooper with Grogu GITD Funko - EE Exclusive
short_description: Get your hands on this Entertainment Earth Exclusive Funko Pop! featuring the menacing Dark Trooper carrying Grogu from The Mandalorian series! Boasting a glow-in-the-dark finish, this limited-edition collectible is perfect for any Star Wars fan.
description:
Relive the action-packed moments from The Mandalorian with this exclusive Star Wars: The Mandalorian Dark Trooper with Grogu Glow-in-the-Dark Pop! Vinyl Figure #488 - Entertainment Earth Exclusive. This sought-after Funko Pop! captures the scene of a Dark Trooper carrying Grogu, and includes a cool glow-in-the-dark feature. This brand new figure comes in its original window-box packaging.

Based on Season 2 Episode 6 of the Disney+ series, this collectible is a must-have for any Star Wars enthusiast or Funko collector. Don't miss the chance to own this limited edition piece – add it to your collection today!

Key Features:
* Entertainment Earth Exclusive
* Glow-in-the-Dark Design
* Based on The Mandalorian Series
* Vinyl Figure
* Window-Box Packaging

items.description: Having trouble finding Baby Yoda? This Entertainment Earth Exclusive! Dark Trooper will help! Features glow-in-the-dark deco! Inspired by the Disney+ Star Wars: The Mandalorian series. Entertainment Earth Exclusive! Moff Gideon sends in the notorious Dark Troopers to capture the ultimate bounty - the  asset  known as The Child! Will they succeed? Based on Season 2  Episode 6 of the Disney+ Star Wars: The Mandalorian TV series  this exclusive Funko Pop! Vinyl figure features a Dark Trooper blasting off with a scared Grogu in hand. It even features glow-in-the-dark deco! Measuring roughly 3 3/4-inches tall  the Star Wars: The Mandalorian Dark Trooper with Grogu Glow-in-the-Dark Pop! Vinyl Figure #488 - Entertainment Earth Exclusive comes in window-box packaging. Order yours today! Grogu is known by many names - The Child  Baby Yoda  kid - but you probably know him best as the pint-sized Force-wielding hero in The Mandalorian whose origins are not completely clear.
